Rating: 1
I made this exactly by the recipe. We didn't care for it, but maybe that is just our individual tastes. If you do make it, the cook times need to be increased to get the potatoes done. 3 1/4 pounds of potatoes are more that you will need for the 9" pan. I had about a pound left over. Personally, I think it needs more salt and pepper.

